45:17.725 --> 45:23.564
But they use a sesame seed bun.
My buns have no seeds.

45:25.649 --> 45:28.319
I've got it.

45:31.196 --> 45:35.534
You've got to mop the food-prep area
twice a day.

45:35.743 --> 45:39.288
- Do you know how to mop?
- Yes, of course.

