46:00.517 --> 46:04.772
When you get through here,
you take out the trash.

46:04.980 --> 46:08.817
Come with me,
I've got an easy job for you.

46:39.473 --> 46:43.352
- Hi!
- Hello.

46:45.688 --> 46:47.940
Hello.

46:48.899 --> 46:51.360
Hi...

46:52.486 --> 46:54.947
I am Akeem.

46:56.574 --> 46:59.702
It's nice to meet you, Akeem.

46:59.910 --> 47:05.374
I've been placed in charge of garbage.
Do you have any that needs disposal

47:05.583 --> 47:08.836
